{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"895e7c82c1","title":"同意拨付农业合作社干部训练费和农业贷款的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1a048630fc","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":1,"articleId":"895e7c82c1"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"f4bd1c9159","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中共广东省委1955年8月23日关于1956年农业社干部的训练经费与贷款给中央的请示报告上。报告说，广东省于1956年春耕前计划发展到7万个社，建社骨干的训练费需127.6万元：1956年新社与老社的巩固工作，又需训练费118.3万元。以上两项共需约246万元，需请中央拨付。另外，为解决新建社的贫农合作基金贷款，以及必要的基建、副业生产和开耕的生产费用，共需贷款3783万元，也需中央予以解决。"},{"id":"0f3accda7b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"小平，即邓小平，当时任中共中央秘书长、国务院副总理。"},{"id":"04ed686a30","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"子恢，即邓子恢，当时任中共中央农村工作部部长、国务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"633e5659f7","type":"title","text":"同意拨付农业合作社干部训练费和农业贷款的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1"},{"id":"f4bd1c9159","type":"paragraph","text":"小平同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1"},{"id":"0f3accda7b","type":"paragraph","text":"这类电报须速复，请告子恢办理。广东所提要求我看是合理的。照此计算，全国每年须付干部训练费约五千方元左右，在几年内每年须付贷款五亿元左右，付出这两笔钱是值得的","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1"},{"id":"04ed686a30","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"895e7c82c1"},{"id":"7f1af69664","type":"paragraph","text":"九月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoq